arts.ttl: Al-Ittihad complete comeback to beat Al-Nassr 3-2
arts.sum: Houssem Aouar scored a last-minute goal to help Al-Ittihad complete a comeback and secure a 3-2 win over Al-Nassr on Wednesday, taking them a step closer to clinching the Saudi Pro League title. Read more at straitstimes.com. Read more at straitstimes.com.
